scron - simple cron daemon
==========================

about
-----
author: Ari Malinen
license: BSD 2-clause
git: https://github.com/defer-/scron

features
--------
Schedule tasks.
Single daemon, config and initscript.
Log to stdout and syslog.
Good error handling.

usage
-----
usage: cron [options]
-h        help
-d        daemon
-f <file> config file

config
------
# tm_min, tm_hour, tm_mday, tm_mon, tm_wday, command
0	5	*	*	*	updatedb
